data.description: Welcome to your cottage home nestled on 5.52 acres with Chickasabogue creek through the back of your property. This 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom has 3,562 square feet of living space, a bonus room upstairs. With four bedrooms, there's no shortage of space for your family and guests. Two primary suites on the main level of home. The first primary suite is oversized with its 2 closets and large bathroom. The 2nd primary bedroom with full bathroom can be found close to your two-car garage entrance.  The additional bedrooms are equally comfortable with large closets.   One of the standout features of this property is the sunroom, where you'll feel like you're nestled in the woods as you sip your morning coffee or enjoy a good book. The Living room has a wood burning fireplace with built in storage around it. Kitchen has Oak cabinets with a large pantry for all your storage needs. Plenty of parking with your circle driveway and a driveway to the garage. The 29 x 47-foot barn with power sets the stage for the incredible potential that comes with this property. Whether you dream of a workshop, hobby space, or storage for your outdoor gear, this barn offers endless possibilities. Plenty of room for horses or gardens whatever your hobby is. This cozy cottage-style home is not just a residence; it's an invitation to a place where you can create lasting memories. "AS IS" Condition. All measurements are approximate and not guaranteed! The Seller’s information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed! All items deemed important are to be verified by the buyers and/or the buyer’s agent.
